Shawarma photo wellplated.com Shawarma is one of the favourite snacks for most Nigerians. It is also very easy to make. Below are the ingredients for Shawarma and how to make Shawarma: Mayonnaise Thai Sweet Chilli Sauce or any Sweet Chilli Sauce Ketchup Salad Cream Parsley Your Shawarma is ready to be eaten. Yummy!  